e amount incurred or paid by or on behalf of the Company or its Subsidiaries shall be included as a current liability in the calculation of Net Working Capital as of 11:59 p.m. on the Closing Date unless such items are included in the calculation of Aggregate Closing Consideration, it being the intent of the parties that no component of Transaction Payments, Indebtedness or Transaction Expenses be duplicated in the calculation of Aggregate Closing Consideration.
