ITEM 7.01  REGULATION FD DISCLOSURE
 
Arkansas Best Corporation ("ABC") (Nasdaq: ABFS) acknowledged today, in response to a third-party inquiry, that in late March, YRC Worldwide Inc. ("YRC") approached ABC and expressed YRC's interest in exploring an acquisition of ABF Freight System, Inc. ("ABF"). ABF is ABC's largest subsidiary.  In early April, ABC advised YRC that ABF was highly focused on its ongoing labor negotiations as well as other strategic and operational initiatives and that considering a transaction with YRC was not appropriate at that time. ABC has not engaged in any subsequent discussions with YRC.
 
